## 📌 Project Overview

This project demonstrates the design of a compact **ESP32-based Temperature and Humidity Monitoring PCB** using the **DHT11 sensor**. The PCB is designed in **KiCad** and provides an easy interface between the ESP32 development board and the DHT11 sensor for environmental monitoring applications.

---

## ✨ Features

- ESP32 DevKit compatible
- DHT11 Temperature & Humidity Sensor Interface
- Compact PCB Layout
- Single-layer PCB Design
- Easy sensor connectivity
- Designed using KiCad

